  "rationale": "This supervisor prioritizes rapid marker acquisition and approach while ensuring obstacle safety and avoiding oscillatory or ambiguous actions. It uses helper states for action commits, marker tracking, and recovery. After obstacle encounters, recovery always passes through a scan/search state before resuming exploration. Marker tracking is robust: loss triggers a scan, and approach continues until the goal is reached. Only one controllable is enabled per state (except in justified recovery cases). All uncontrollables are total, and transitions are deterministic.",
