  "strategy": [
    "In clear, prefer move_forward to advance, but allow marker tracking if marker_seen.",
    "On marker_seen, immediately switch to marker_track to prioritize goal-seeking.",
    "In marker_track, use move_to_marker as the primary action; if marker_lost, initiate scan_full to reacquire.",
    "If marker_close occurs in any state, transition to goal_stop and only allow stop.",
    "Obstacle events always preempt and transition to the corresponding obs_* state.",
    "In obs_left, prefer rotate_clockwise; in obs_right, prefer rotate_counterclockwise for escape.",
    "After obs_front, use full_rotate (scan_full) for recovery, ensuring a scan before resuming exploration.",
    "All commit states (forward_commit, rotate_commit_*) are one-shot: after the action, return to clear or perception state.",
    "After any recovery or scan, always pass through scan_full or clear before resuming forward exploration.",
    "No oscillatory or ambiguous controllable choices in any state."
  ]
